  Inventory Message
The item you just added was instantly added to all of the stores in your chain with the exception of the Qty on Hand field.

If a store already had this SKU in the system, then only a few fields will be overridden at the store level:

Description
Department
Style & Size (If appliciable)
Reorder & Normal Qty Level (If appliciable)

All inventory changes are automatically logged in the 'Security Log' tab of that item, per store.
  Compatibility Message
This advanced feature must be enabled in the Global Setup / Discount Groups Tab. If enabled this allows a store to apply an automatic discount once a predetermined number of qualifying items are sold.

Buy six items (set by the store) including mix and match and automatically get a 10% discount or $ 2.00 off.
  Compatibility Message
In order to have the ability for a clerk to quickly touch and scroll through the inventory you must activate this in Global Settings / POS Options.

This feature is designed for items that are consistently sold and don't have a bar-code.
